divs: Sighting DetailsI saw this object at 9am in Englewood, Co. The object was stationary for about 1 hour. I took photos of this object and they are very strange. It looks like a fireball and part of a saucer. It then started to move at super sonic speed when a jet was flying towards it. It then disapeared into the sky. I was on my way to work when I got out of my truck and saw the object. The photos attached would need to be zoomed in to see the definition of the object.
